305
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,320
Even a laymen like me

306
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,120
finds it truly impressive.

307
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:52,960
Now,

308
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,510
