makeup training?

318
00:13:12,550 --> 00:13:13,120
Don't worry.

319
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:13,670
That's okay.

320
00:13:22,550 --> 00:13:23,630
Jiang Xiaoyuan?

321
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,510
Yes, ma'am.

322
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:28,030
